      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Dataset**"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "np.random.seed(42)\n",
        "\n",
        "departments = [\n",
        "    \"Cardiology\", \"Orthopedics\", \"Neurology\",\n",
        "    \"Pediatrics\", \"General Medicine\", \"Dermatology\"\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "num_records = 1200\n",
        "\n",
        "patient_ids = np.arange(1, num_records + 1)\n",
        "\n",
        "appointment_times = pd.date_range(\n",
        "    start=\"2025-01-01 08:00\",\n",
        "    periods=num_records,\n",
        "    freq=\"15min\"\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "arrival_offset = np.random.randint(-15, 20, num_records)\n",
        "consult_delay = np.random.randint(5, 40, num_records)\n",
        "\n",
        "arrival_times = appointment_times + pd.to_timedelta(arrival_offset, unit=\"m\")\n",
        "consultation_start = arrival_times + pd.to_timedelta(consult_delay, unit=\"m\")\n",
        "\n",
        "df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "    \"Patient_ID\": patient_ids,\n",
        "    \"Department\": np.random.choice(departments, num_records),\n",
        "    \"Appointment_Time\": appointment_times,\n",
        "    \"Arrival_Time\": arrival_times,\n",
        "    \"Consultation_Start\": consultation_start\n",
        "})\n",
        "\n",
        "df.head()\n"
      ],

      "source": [

      "source": [

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
